Compilation / installation:
./configure && make && make install.

Compilation options:
--prefix          to choose the installation directory
--with-syslog     for eneble / disable syslog support (enabled by default)

System integration
the soft is daemon running by default
for laun,ching this at os start a simple script like this is necessary:

#!/bin/bash
case "$1" in
	start)
	/path/to/bin/arpalert
	;;
	
	stop)
	kill -TERM `cat /path/to/lockfile/lock`
	;;
	
	restart)
	kill -TERM `cat /path/to/lockfile/lock`
	/path/to/bin/arpalert
	;;
	
	reload)
	kill -HUP `cat /path/to/lockfile/lock`
	;;

	*)
	echo "Usage: $0 {start|stop|restart|reload}
	;;
esac
